name: END1
text: Clinical status assessed using a 7-category ordinal scale at Day 28

name: END2
text: Time to clinical improvement (TTCI) defined as a National Early Warning Score 2 (NEWS2) of <=2 maintained for 24 hours

name: END3
text: Time to improvement of at least 2 categories relative to baseline on a 7-category ordinal scale of clinical status
